cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about image set classification using a Riemannian manifold network. The most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as the paper deals with image classification. The second likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper proposes a new learning method. The third likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper deals with a non-linear learning method. The fourth likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as the paper proposes a neural network architecture. The fifth likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia) as the paper deals with video-based face recognition and set-based object categorization.
